{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Intricate Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0347.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Detective Hakeem, a detective with the local law enforcement who has been sent to investigate the death of the wealthy heir, only to find out that he was expected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speak with suspects, investigate the environment, and solve the many puzzles left behind b y Amir to uncover Amir and his guests' entangled past and what transpired during his last party. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Inspired Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0345.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the environment to solve puzzles and find hidden clues throughout Amir\u2019s mansion. Speak with suspects to be transported into a recreation of the events from their point of view, where you will be able to find discrepancies to help you find the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse Set of Suspects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0354.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speak with six different suspects, all carefully curated and written, who share an elaborate and sometimes interconnected past, all with motives not only to kill Amir, but to throw each other under the bus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Elaborate Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0341.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Due to the family\u2019s expensive taste, Amir\u2019s mansion is full of beautiful pieces filling its many rooms, but due to Amir\u2019s own secretive ways, there is so much more than meets the eye; some beautiful ornate pieces could hold secrets Amir never shared with anyone! </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736418417","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736418417","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/207628c441bc62d8f5f448eb081d7fb021505636/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736418417","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/207628c441bc62d8f5f448eb081d7fb021505636/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736418417","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/8-fbtw.png?t=1736418417\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Intricate Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0347.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Detective Hakeem, a detective with the local law enforcement who has been sent to investigate the death of the wealthy heir, only to find out that he was expected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speak with suspects, investigate the environment, and solve the many puzzles left behind b y Amir to uncover Amir and his guests' entangled past and what transpired during his last party. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Inspired Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0345.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the environment to solve puzzles and find hidden clues throughout Amir\u2019s mansion. Speak with suspects to be transported into a recreation of the events from their point of view, where you will be able to find discrepancies to help you find the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse Set of Suspects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0354.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speak with six different suspects, all carefully curated and written, who share an elaborate and sometimes interconnected past, all with motives not only to kill Amir, but to throw each other under the bus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Elaborate Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/extras/IMG_0341.gif?t=1736418417\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Due to the family\u2019s expensive taste, Amir\u2019s mansion is full of beautiful pieces filling its many rooms, but due to Amir\u2019s own secretive ways, there is so much more than meets the eye; some beautiful ornate pieces could hold secrets Amir never shared with anyone! </p>","developers":["Lucky 7 Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985760/header.jpg?t=1736418417","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257047523,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047523/movie480.mp4?t=1724075730","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257047523/movie_max.mp4?t=1724075730"},"name":"F